com.mparticle

Interface MParticle.UserAttributes

  • Enclosing class:
    MParticle

    public static interface MParticle.UserAttributes
    This interface defines a series of constants that can be used to specify certain characteristics of a user. There are many 3rd party services that support, for example, specifying a gender of a user. The mParticle platform will look for these constants within the user attributes that you have set for a given user, and forward any attributes to the services that support them.
    See Also:
    MParticleUser
